Alembic migrations for Insider Tracker.

DATABASE_URL must be set in the environment before running migrations:
  export DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:pass@localhost:5432/insider_tracker

Common commands:
  alembic upgrade head          # apply all pending migrations
  alembic current               # show current revision
  alembic history --verbose     # show all revisions
  alembic downgrade -1          # roll back one migration

This project uses raw SQL (op.execute) rather than SQLAlchemy ORM models.
The schema is the authoritative definition of the PostgreSQL tables —
ingest.py's SCHEMA string is now SQLite-only (legacy reference).
